<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Invoice</title>
    <style>
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <main class="container">
        <h1>Booking Invoice</h1>
        <p>Booking Date: <%= bookingDate %></p>
        <p>Tour Name: <%= tourName %></p>
        <p>Number of Guests: <%= guestCount %></p>
        <p>Total Amount: <%= totalAmount %></p>
        <p>Transaction ID: <%= transactionId %></p>
        <p>Hey <b><%= recieverName %></b>,</p>
        <p>
            <b>Thank you for booking with us!</b>
        </p>
        <p>
            <code>We have attached the invoice of your booking. Please keep it safe as it is your records.</code>
        </p>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>© 2025 Tour Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>